~]$ cat glusterfs-hadoop/src/main/java/org/apache/hadoop/fs/glusterfs/Util.java
Util.java
...
import org.apache.hadoop.fs.FileUtil;
...

public class Util{
...
}

So all affected code is outside of rhs-hadoop package
